From d1874e6effdfd47f1bce0cc8802a2dd15e45051c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Bas Nieuwenhuizen <bas@basnieuwenhuizen.nl>
Date: Wed, 2 Sep 2020 14:22:38 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 0795/1714] drm/amd/display: Store tiling_flags in the
 framebuffer.

This moves the tiling_flags to the framebuffer creation.
This way the time of the "tiling" decision is the same as it
would be with modifiers.

Signed-off-by: Bas Nieuwenhuizen <bas@basnieuwenhuizen.nl>
Reviewed-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Nicholas Kazlauskas <nicholas.kazlauskas@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
---
